item.title: TTC Delays
item.description: Introduction In this analyses, we are going to look at the average delay time of TTC subways, streetcars, and buses library(tidyverse) library(blogdown) library(opendatatoronto) library(skimr) library(visdat) subway_error_codes <- search_packages("TTC Subway Delay Data") %>% list_package_resources() %>% filter(name == "ttc-subway-delay-codes") %>% get_resource() ## New names: ## * `` -> ...1 ## * `CODE DESCRIPTION` -> `CODE DESCRIPTION...3` ## * `` -> ...4 ## * `` -> ...5 ## * `CODE DESCRIPTION` -> `CODE DESCRIPTION.
